# Canonical security headers — the SINGLE source of truth, imported by both the
# Compose Caddyfile and the Kubernetes Caddyfile (caddy/Caddyfile{,.k8s}). This is
# what replaced the old two-places duplication (nginx/security_headers.conf AND the
# Helm ingress configuration-snippet) that #188 set out to remove.
#
# The app emits a *baseline* copy of these too (app/main.py:security_headers, #66) —
# deliberately without script-src/default-src so it can never intersect and break
# this fuller CDN-aware policy. Caddy SETs (replaces) each header here, so exactly one
# canonical value reaches the client even though the upstream sent its baseline.
#
# `defer` is REQUIRED for that "exactly one" guarantee: it runs these header ops AFTER
# reverse_proxy has copied the upstream (app baseline) response headers, so each SET
# overrides the upstream's copy instead of being applied first and then coexisting with
# it — which would ship two CSP / HSTS values. The block also happens to defer implicitly
# because it contains a delete op (`-Server`), but relying on that is fragile: removing
# `-Server` would silently reintroduce the duplicate headers. The explicit `defer` makes
# the guarantee robust to future edits (#201).
#
# The script-src sha256 hash pins the one inline bootstrap script in base.html; if that
# script changes, regenerate the hash (see .claude/rules/frontend.md) and update it here.
header {
	defer
	Content-Security-Policy "default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'sha256-+Eb7yRWu45ifRb64zPIDP0hvsT4OloSS8kNklIXpCO4=' https://cdn.tailwindcss.com https://cdn.jsdelivr.net; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' data:; connect-src 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; object-src 'none'; form-action 'self'"
	Strict-Transport-Security "max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload"
	X-Content-Type-Options "nosniff"
	X-Frame-Options "DENY"
	Referrer-Policy "same-origin"
	Permissions-Policy "accelerometer=(), camera=(), geolocation=(), gyroscope=(), magnetometer=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=()"
	# Don't advertise the server software (parity with nginx `server_tokens off`).
	-Server
}
